import pandas as pd
keys = []
values = []

for line in lines:
    parts = line.split(':', 1) 
    key = parts[0].strip() + ':'
    value = parts[1].strip() if len(parts) > 1 else ''  
    keys.append(key)
    values.append(value)

df = pd.DataFrame({'Keys': keys, 'Values': values})
df
